|               |  Limit: skip=0, fetch=10                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |
|               |   Projection: hits.SearchPhrase                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |     Sort: to_timestamp(hits.EventTime) ASC NULLS LAST, hits.SearchPhrase ASC NULLS LAST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
