|               |         Filter: CAST(hits.SearchPhrase AS Utf8View) != Utf8("")                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
|               |           TableScan: hits projection=[EventTime, SearchPhrase]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
